-- Burger King extends late night hours
-- 
-- Fri May 30, 2008 9:49am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/30/us-burgerking-idUSWNAS614520080530

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Burger King Corp BKC.N said on Friday that starting June 5, its U.S. restaurants will be open until 2 a.m. or later Thursday through Saturday. 

 The hamburger chain said it is launching a television advertising spot featuring hip-hop impresario Sean Combs to promote the extended hours. (Reporting by  Nicole Maestri , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)